    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean by \"let the weight go\"? i don't think i have the strength to just \"reclaim\" anything. it feels like the person who did that work is dead anyway. the \"me\" that existed was tied to the research. without it, i'm just a shell.",
