      "content": "a \"necessary ending\"... that sounds almost peaceful, in a dark way. but isn't that just a euphemism for giving up? i don't know if i'm allowed to just stop. everyone expects me to keep trying, to pivot, to find some new \"purpose.\" but i don't see the point in pretending anymore.",
